  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the heart of Paris with <i>Cafe Paris</i>, a 3D endless coffee shop simulator where coffee, food, and stories come together. Located between the foot of the Eiffel Tower and the banks of the Seine, <i>Cafe Paris</i> is a 24/7 café bustling with customers from all walks of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you run “Cafe Paris,” serving up perfectly brewed coffee and freshly made pastries to an ever-changing cast of characters. As day turns to night and back again, you’ll get to know your customers, each with their own stories to tell.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Greet and serve customers arriving around the clock.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.webm?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.mp4?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of coffee-making and food preparation, tailored to each order.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/ac1a171b98ace046523049c5408d4abd.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/ac1a171b98ace046523049c5408d4abd.webm?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/ac1a171b98ace046523049c5408d4abd.mp4?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soak in the authentic atmosphere of Paris, with views of the Eiffel Tower as your backdrop.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/00374f9e2f760626342470e6ab4964f7.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/00374f9e2f760626342470e6ab4964f7.webm?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/00374f9e2f760626342470e6ab4964f7.mp4?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a café like no other, where every cup, pastry, and conversation brings you closer to the heart of Paris.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/c97bd121688763e348a2b833a1a040b4.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/c97bd121688763e348a2b833a1a040b4.webm?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/c97bd121688763e348a2b833a1a040b4.mp4?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the heart of Paris with <i>Cafe Paris</i>, a 3D endless coffee shop simulator where coffee, food, and stories come together. Located between the foot of the Eiffel Tower and the banks of the Seine, <i>Cafe Paris</i> is a 24/7 café bustling with customers from all walks of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you run “Cafe Paris,” serving up perfectly brewed coffee and freshly made pastries to an ever-changing cast of characters. As day turns to night and back again, you’ll get to know your customers, each with their own stories to tell.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Greet and serve customers arriving around the clock.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.webm?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/8028e68939f6d8c869df71fc4f3f97a4.mp4?t=1745354659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the art of coffee-making and food preparation, tailored to each order.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/ac1a171b98ace046523049c5408d4abd.poster.avif?t=1745354659\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1612330/extras/ac